spec: concurrent_futures_extra132
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(concurrent.futures)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/concurrent.futures.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/concurrent.futures.html — Python concurrent.futures module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/concurrent/futures/_base.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: wave 258 theme — concurrent.futures.as_completed and concurrent.futures.wait function qualnames, co_argcount, and co_varnames. NEW in extra132: concurrent.futures.as_completed.__qualname__=='as_completed' (len=12); concurrent.futures.as_completed.__module__=='concurrent.futures._base' (len=24); concurrent.futures.as_completed.__code__.co_argcount==2 (fs, timeout); concurrent.futures.as_completed.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==9; concurrent.futures.wait.__qualname__=='wait' (len=4); concurrent.futures.wait.__module__=='concurrent.futures._base' (len=24); concurrent.futures.wait.__code__.co_argcount==3 (fs, timeout, return_when); concurrent.futures.wait.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==7; concurrent.futures.ProcessPoolExecutor.__init__.__qualname__=='ProcessPoolExecutor.__init__' (len=28); concurrent.futures.ProcessPoolExecutor.__module__=='concurrent.futures.process' (len=26); concurrent.futures.ProcessPoolExecutor.__mro__.__len__()==3. All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "concurrent.futures.as_completed is a generator function (inspect.isgeneratorfunction returns True). Its co_varnames are ('fs', 'timeout', 'end_time', 'total_futures', 'finished', 'pending', 'waiter', 'wait_timeout', 'f') — 2 parameters + 7 local variables. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "concurrent.futures.wait is NOT a generator function — it returns a named tuple (done, not_done). Its co_varnames are ('fs', 'timeout', 'return_when', 'f', 'done', 'not_done', 'waiter') — 3 parameters + 4 local variables. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "concurrent.futures.ProcessPoolExecutor.__module__ == 'concurrent.futures.process' (len=26: 'concurrent'=10+'.'=1+'futures'=7+'.'=1+'process'=7=26). This is one char longer than ThreadPoolExecutor.__module__ ('concurrent.futures.thread', len=25). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
